<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Stone2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Stone,</orth> vb. 1) to pelt or kill with stones: <bibl n="shak. luc 978" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 978</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.807" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 807</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.807" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 807</bibl><lb />2) to make like stone, to harden: <cit><quote>thou dost s. my heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 63</bibl></cit>.
